{"tid":962972,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"世界上最大既騙局","createTime":"2018-12-31T09:18:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T12:15:10.000Z","uid":158145,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4b9a80d32efbe9c01e9f20aa25bec91240d90ce4","tid":962972,"uid":158145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T09:18:17.000Z","msg":"&lt;打籃球會變高&gt;<br />\n好多人見到專業既籃球員可以咁高就以為打籃球打得多就會高，根本佢地本身就已經比正常人高，所以先被人招攬做專業籃球員。<br />\n有部分專業籃球員身高可能比較矮，唔通佢地打籃球比其他人少？咩？<br />\n由此可見，打籃球係唔會變高。"},{"pid":"371ef4314f8f69591bde237e7dbf5bacb4ddbf06","tid":962972,"uid":179137,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T09:19:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f29a3804ab244b690b81cc3445559cf326809cad","tid":962972,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T09:21:41.000Z","msg":"同守龍一樣道理<br />\n我成日猜輸做龍 又唔見會激發我生得高"},{"pid":"3b266223e1173e1836ecda5c49c33dad15c864b2","tid":962972,"uid":172613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f29a3804ab244b690b81cc3445559cf326809cad","tid":962972,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T09:21:41.000Z","msg":"同守龍一樣道理<br />\n我成日猜輸做龍 又唔見會激發我生得高"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T09:25:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f23d37844591d8db0bc11602b2db403b62acf7","tid":962972,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"3b266223e1173e1836ecda5c49c33dad15c864b2","tid":962972,"uid":172613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f29a3804ab244b690b81cc3445559cf326809cad","tid":962972,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T09:21:41.000Z","msg":"同守龍一樣道理<br />\n我成日猜輸做龍 又唔見會激發我生得高"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T09:25:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"c